**PTE-001:** A man standing against the rolling thunder of the west, a fortunate son in the eyes of a loving mother. Mocked and dismissed in a palace three tens before in the eyes of men of paling skin. Scorned twice, enough is enough and agreements signed by bloodied pens for cooperation ultimately fail in search of self-identification. Elected to lead his people, colonizers and exploiters everywhere, total war extends and jungle and rice fields burn. In a valley fortress surrounded by jungle, those who claim what is not theirs will meet the end of an empire in a night of blood and fire. 



