**1000-1020:** At approximately 1000 hours SCP-001 looks up in the general direction of the sky. The buzz of a multi-propeller plane becomes audible. More upward facing cameras capture a C-47 appearing from the southeast. SCP-001 continues to look up for the next twenty minutes, its head tracking the plane until it disappears into the low clouds around the mountains. 



**1021-1051:** Echoes of metal scraping faintly against rock are picked up by camera microphones, followed by a much fainter crack. SCP-001’s shoulders slowly slump, and it continues to drink from the mug for the next half hour. It returns to the building at 1051 hours with its head raised, but eyes closed.



